\id JDG - Havai 
\h Tangaloi Vagamwasoi 
\toc1 Tangaloi Vagamwasoi 
\toc2 Tangaloi Vagamwasoi 
\toc3 TVA 
\mt1 Tangaloi Vagamwasoi 
\c 2  
\s1 Israel He Huri \nd Huqe\nd* Tea 
\p  
\v 6 Jesua mo hora vohogi na tangaloi tau Israel. Gagategalegi vin vano vin lei na vanue ngehi vin vuragi na nona hagogineu.  
\v 7 Me a tangaloi ram galohagi na \nd Huqe\nd* lolo taro tavohe i Jesua u mwaso. Lo tagui taro noi Jesua, ram galohagi \nd Huqe\nd* tau duruhi na taro nora sesea ngerehi rau lehi na tabana lawua doluegi ngehi \nd Huqe\nd* uvei beno lawera Israel.  
\v 8 Jesua netui Nun, tangaloi tabana noi \nd Huqe,\nd* u mate lo higaona vudolue avigi hangavulu.  
\v 9 Siu ram tulegi nie lolo vanue hi a nona lo Timnat Heres, lolo vusi tanoi Evrem, gangarani lo Vusi Gaas. 
\p  
\v 10 Siu lo babagi leheno mei Jesua rau mate beno, me ngerehi rau vora lo tagugi hateve rau ilo \nd Huqe\nd* mena tabana lawua ngehi u veiana beno lawera Israel. 
\p  
\v 11 Siu tangaloi tau Israel ram vai na gineu esi lolo matai nora \nd Huqe\nd* me ram tabana noi tagaro vurogi saosao.  
\v 12 Ram siregi na \nd Huqe\nd* a Huqe noi retubure, ngehi u lei vohogi nire dena vanue Ijib. Ngerehi ru vora atagu ram huri na huqe wagineu nora tangaloi doluegi ngehi dalire, me ram huduhudu lawera. Ram vai na \nd Huqe\nd* mo mero‪‬,  
\v 13 huri ram siregi Huqe me ram tabana noi Tagaro me ngere huqe vavinegi.  
\v 14 Tavohe \nd Huqe\nd* mo merogi nire Israel mo betera sulo limara tangaloi vuro sao ramo wehire me ramo balu na nora vai gineu. \nd Huqe\nd* mo siregi nire sulo limara nora tavalui vuro ngerehi ram toga dalire. Lo taro hi ngere Israel rahe vai lai tea vena rain labe lo nagoi nora tavalui vuro.  
\v 15 Lo taro hi ram vano lolo vuro, limei \nd Huqe\nd* mo eno vovohire mo vai asisigi nire mwere hi nge u veve me u haharigi. U gagarasi lawuagi lawera tau Israel. 
\p  
\v 16 Siu me \nd Huqe\nd* mo ragasire na tangaloi vagamwasoi me ramo vagamwasoire Israel dena limara tangaloi vuro.  
\v 17 Me tangaloi tau Israel hateve rau rongo na leo nora tangaloi vagamwasoi, me ram dori mwere na vavine huri turegi lo tagure huqe wagineu me ram huduhudu lawera. Ram begi siseri dena turegi ngehi retubure rau dige lune me rai ronghuri leo hora noi \nd Huqe\nd* tea.  
\v 18 Lo taro hi \nd Huqe\nd* mo ragasi na nora tangaloi vagamwasoi, \nd Huqe\nd* mo toga meire tangaloi vagamwasoi. Ngeie mo vagamwasoire dena limei nora tavalui vuro lolo taro nora tangaloi vagamwasoi, huri \nd Huqe\nd* mo hagavire lo taroi nora raveana huri ngerehi ram vai asisigi nire me ram vai gagarasigi nire.  
\v 19 Me lo taro hi tangaloi vagamwasoi u mate, me ram tudori ramo vai gineu rau esi liu retubure. Ram dige mo hurire huqe wagineu vena rain tabana nora, me vena rain huduhudu lawera. Ram rao siregi na nora doridori esi mena turegi na qatusiaga. 
\p  
\v 20 Mo vai i \nd Huqe\nd* mo mero lawuagi meire Israel me mo veve vena, “Huri a sinobu lehe he huri na nogu waratau siaga tea hi nau veve lawe tubure me hateve rau ronghuri na dilogu,  
\v 21 siu neu nain he livusi na buri sinobu lehe tea ngerehi ram toga mwaso mosigei tavohe Jesua u mate beno.  
\v 22 Neu nain veire huri siu rain vailehire Israel vena ngere Israel rain huri na nogu turegi me rain dige lune mwerei retubure sige hatie.” 
\p  
\v 23 Me \nd Huqe\nd* mo siregi na buri sinobu hi ram toga. Nge he livusire tea vena siseri, me hateve u betera sulo limei Jesua. 
\c 3  
\p  
\v 1 Ngelehe buri sinobu ngehi \nd Huqe\nd* u siregi nire rau tirendu, nge mo vailehire doluegi tau Israel lure. Ngerehi Israel rau mwaso lo taro hi rai ilo na vuro tea lolo vanue Kenan  
\v 2 (nge hogosie mo huhui reneture Israel ve rain vei vuro mwere hi rai ilo na vai vuro tea lo taro vano beno):  
\v 3 Ngere ratahigi gailime nora tau Balistaen, meire ngere tau Kenan, meire tau Sidon, meire tau Hivi ngehi rau toga lo vusi sao Lebenon tavuigi lo Vusi Bal Heremon mo dadari Lebo Hamat.  
\v 4 Sinobu ngerehi ram toga vena ngeie vin vailehire tau Israel vena ngere rain tabe na leohora noi \nd Huqe\nd* ngehi ngeie u bete lawe retubure duruhi Mosis sige hatie.  
\v 5 Tangaloi tau Israel ram toga lo livugara tau Kenan, meire tau Hiti, meire tau Amoro, meire tau Beris, meire tau Hivi, meire tau Jebus.  
\v 6 Ngere Israel ram lai reneture vavine vuragi gaihorara, me ngere Israel ram bete reneture vavine lawe reneture mwera ngere talo tavalugi ram vuragi gaihorara. Me ngere Israel ram maraga ram tabana noi nora huqe sao.